{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "b67e3615-e90b-4067-9ef5-746640e039c9", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/b67e3615-e90b-4067-9ef5-746640e039c9@1.pkg/1772597577619/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597578522", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/b67e3615-e90b-4067-9ef5-746640e039c9@1.pkg/1772597577619/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597578522"}, "identifier": "b67e3615-e90b-4067-9ef5-746640e039c9", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>本题考查对学无止境、终身学习的理解。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">②③：</span><span>《中国教育现代化 2035》的目标强调了学习对国家和个人的重要性，树立终身学习理念、培养批判精神都是适应学习型社会的重要素养，符合 &ldquo;学无止境&rdquo; 的要求，故</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">②③</span><span>符合题意；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①</span><span>：&ldquo;拒绝参与任何课外实践活动&rdquo; 错误，实践是学习的重要途径，应将课堂学习与课外实践结合；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">④</span><span>：&ldquo;忽视基础知识积累&rdquo; 错误，基础知识是学习的根基，盲目追求高难度知识不符合科学的学习规律；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>故本题选</span><span>D</span><span>。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">（改编）</span><span>中共中央、国务院印发的《中国教育现代化 2035》明确提出，到 2035 年要让我国迈入教育强国行列，成为学习大国、人力资源强国。这一目标的实现，需要每一个人在学习道路上持续努力。为此，我们应（ ）</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>①专注课堂学习，拒绝参与任何课外实践活动</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>②树立终身学习理念，始终保持对知识的探索欲</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>③在学习中培养批判精神，敢于质疑不合理的观点</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>④忽视基础知识积累，一味追求高难度知识的学习</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（改编）中共中央、国务院印发的《中国教育现代化 2035》明确提出，到 2035 年要让我国迈入教育强国行列，成为学习大国、人力资源强国。这一目标的实现，需要每一个人在学习道路上持续努力。为此，我们应（ ）①专注课堂学习，拒绝参与任何课外实践活动②树立终身学习理念，始终保持对知识的探索欲③在学习中培养批判精神，敢于质疑不合理的观点④忽视基础知识积累，一味追求高难度知识的学习", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["D"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/b67e3615-e90b-4067-9ef5-746640e039c9@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754984621140", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①②&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">③④&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①④&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">②③</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">（改编）</span><span>中共中央、国务院印发的《中国教育现代化 2035》明确提出，到 2035 年要让我国迈入教育强国行列，成为学习大国、人力资源强国。这一目标的实现，需要每一个人在学习道路上持续努力。为此，我们应（ ）</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>①专注课堂学习，拒绝参与任何课外实践活动</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>②树立终身学习理念，始终保持对知识的探索欲</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>③在学习中培养批判精神，敢于质疑不合理的观点</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>④忽视基础知识积累，一味追求高难度知识的学习</span></p></div>", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "44bec0c6-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "5036342749", "$RE0200", "6a74973a-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "44bec0c6-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a74973a-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5"], "status": "ONLINE", "is_publish": false, "id": "b67e3615-e90b-4067-9ef5-746640e039c9", "global_title": {"zh-CN": "（改编）中共中央、国务院